      "date": "2012-09-20 19:09:46.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64, CentOS release 5.8/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/281210e8-0354-11e2-83cf-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
